text.tspan: Range of ISA modules (base and extensions) initially enabled by -march=*
Incremental changes to the target ISA made by extended options, such as -mfpu=*
* In this configuration model, there is no essential
difference between new ISA extensions and incremental
updates to existing ISA components. However, new
extended options that alters the range of enabled ISA
modules may be added in future updates, and their
semantics may be specific to one of these two dimensions.
